headline.print_headline: E.P.A. Will Put Bigger Trucks on a Fuel Diet

lead_paragraph: The Environmental Protection Agency is expected to propose rules requiring heavy trucks to increase their fuel economy by up to 40 percent by 2027.

headline.main: The World’s Coming Broadband Divide
headline.print_headline: A New World Divide On Broadband Lines

snippet: Ultrafast Internet access is spreading unevenly throughout the world. And not getting that kind of broadband access could mean some communities miss out on significant economic opportunity.
